channel.title: Odd issue? [Port Forwarding]
channel.description:
My dad picked up a signal booster for our phones since where I live our cell phones don't pick up very good signal. Anyways, I believe this is the source of my problem. I've never in my years of RSPS had any issues with port forwarding. So don't tell me I didn't do it right, I did. I'm just looking for some possible solutions. Thanks.
Additional info: I had the server port forwarded and it was working fine until he plugged the booster in.
